    "en": {
      "title": "A thousand tons of Chinese rice arrived",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Chinese embassy has announced that 500 metric tons of rice in two batches worth 500 million yuan have been handed over to Sri Lanka.",
        "Accordingly, the Chinese ambassador to Sri Lanka has mentioned this on his official Twitter page that the first batch arrived in Colombo on the 16th and the second batch on the 19th. Among them, 3,000 metric tons of rice for 1.1 million children in 7,900 schools have been handed over to the Ministry of Education under the school feeding program."
      ],
